      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Looks hard to go past the Petrick yard saddling up two top chances. REWARDS AND MORE (3) led last time and was just run down late over 1100m. That was the first run for the new yard. Better for it and will take catching. OUR COUVER (4) returns from a break and looks well placed. Yet to win fresh but has a great record course and distance and rates highly this line-up. Looks the danger. O'TYCOON (2) returns to the Whittle yard after a stint in SA and also returns from a break. He has a good record fresh and at the course and distance. Serious threat. BOY BIG (5) is a veteran with a great record this course and distance and looks a top three chance. FLYING YISHU (1) rates highly on strong second-up record and should improve on the fresh-up fifth.",
